docs.title: What is KYC ⁉️
docs.text: KYC stands for "Know Your Customer" and refers to mandatory customer authentication in various institutions and companies. This authentication includes your personal information to confirm your identity. You can use a valid ID card, passport, bank statement, and various bills for authentication. If authentication is not performed, some features of that institution or company may not be accessible.
